# Media drop-zone

Put user-supplied README media here. Placeholders referenced from ../../README.md:
- hero.png (hero image — Pressed Album export or Garden beauty shot)
- kindle-walkthrough.png (Finder screenshot of Kindle volume)
- site-config-edit.png (screenshot of site.config.ts fields)

These are gitignored by default if you drop personal screenshots — the
.gitkeep keeps the directory in the tree.

